snippet.title: What Must Be Done - Gameplay - Ludum Dare 52 game jam
snippet.description:
What Must Be Done was made in 72 hours for the Ludum Dare 52 game jam.
- Play the game! (https://drgvdg.itch.io/what-must-be-done)
- Check-out the Ludum Dare reviews! (https://ldjam.com/events/ludum-dare/52/what-must-be-done)
- Made with Godot! (https://godotengine.org/)
